                    </a></div></div></div><div class="table-full-width-wrap"><div class="table-wrap table-wide standard-table"><div class="table-wrap-title" id="T1" data-id="T1"><span class="label title-label" id="label-94398">Table 1.</span><div class="caption caption-id-" id="caption-94398"><p class="chapter-para">Dominant fields of EU litigation.</p></div> </div><div class="table-overflow"><table role="table" aria-labelledby="&#xA;                        label-94398" aria-describedby="&#xA;                        caption-94398"><thead><tr><th><strong>Field</strong><span aria-hidden="true" style="display: none;">
